<br>
2740*2 + 2740*.2 = 6028, the max hit I've gotten with sos with my gimpy grimoire for a focus :P.<br>
<br>
3000*2 + 3000*.3 = 6900 but this is smaller than my max hit!<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.kane-bayle.com/gallery/images/101.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
7024 here is my current max hit(and it takes a damn long time to produce these when you don't use it primarily)...<br>
<br>
This would lead me to believe that the max hit may be calculated with:<br>
1.3(3000*2) = 7200<br>
<br>
the average hit for furies then would be found with:<br>
<br>
SOM = 1.155(2100*1.2) = 2910.6 (ratio: 4.851)<br>
SOS = .155(2740) + 1.2(2740) = 3712.7 (ratio: 5.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
So it's still lower ratio. Without the mods, SOS:SOM is 1.222:1. With this it's 1.195:1. <br>
<br>
Another look, unmodified dmg,which is likely the nuke's base aggro(or can be compared to this somehow) and can be compared to its modified total.<br>
<br>
SOM:<br>
2910.6/2100(ave)<br>
1.386:1<br>
SOS:<br>
3712.7:2740<br>
1.355:1<br>
<br>
Raw dps with the above figures:<br>
<br>
2910.6/5.85 = 524.45dps<br>
3712.7/7.05 = 526.6dps<br>
<br>
Well it may the the red headed stepchild deserving a buff, but I think this is nice information to know. Correct me if im wrong :P. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=velaelsoulrender>Velael Soulrender</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist<BR>The Snuggly SZ'r!</span><br>  Posts: 1045<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/21/03 12:53:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26189.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Shock of Magic: the crits effected by a DMG focus?</span><hr size=1> Were you grouped with a bard playing Rizlona's? <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-family:courier;font-size:small;">&quot;It never stops hurting, you just go faster...&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> - <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Greg LeMond</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=26189.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=26189.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26189.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.graffe.com/images/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=26189.top